snippet.title: Transport Tycoon - Arriving Soon
snippet.description:
http://www.transporttycoon.com

From Chris Sawyer, creator of TRANSPORT TYCOON and ROLLERCOASTER TYCOON, comes the definitive version of the simulation classic.

Arriving 2013 on iOS and Android platforms.

Follow @TransportTycoon on twitter! ( http://www.twitter.com/TransportTycoon )
